{"tid":747061,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪個個女仔都係咁","createTime":"2018-07-18T05:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T15:15:14.000Z","uid":148718,"like":68,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b6d875bcc1e9d3ecc69cdc97f4aac0a9ce2b3c13","tid":747061,"uid":148718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:38:17.000Z","msg":"同女朋友食飯傾計永遠都有佢講無我講 <br />\n<br />\n即係佢會分享自己返工呀返學呀朋友呀個啲野 我初初有時候覺得無聊都會唔集中呀 hea應 但俾佢屌過 我都覺得佢啱 應該尊重佢<br />\n<br />\n但點解佢永遠都唔會聽我講我既經歷 佢就覺得佢自己既野好有聊 我個啲就無聊？每次同佢傾下我啲野就快速帶過<br />\n琴日同佢食飯我講緊自己今日點 之後俾佢一句 不如我地食乜乜乜打斷 之後我特登唔繼續講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  結果佢無問返 我個刻都無癮繼續講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又要要求我 你又hea鳩我 我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af49cc5c323338c3665acf1bc6e704b1d5f7264","tid":747061,"uid":138138,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/133842_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F133842_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=85e112a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01d05a2a79bb6b6c90b774fe814d4322f1413f56","tid":747061,"uid":1590,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"姐係話佢份人比較自私，同埋你對佢黎講唔係咁重要，佢對你既野冇興趣。<br />\n明唔明？"},{"pid":"f947ed13197c545f7220b5ab15398bdde5d85db7","tid":747061,"uid":29929,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:43:33.000Z","msg":"愛自己多過愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf81ec9c5b8bd4f0218d186f447756a2be346e96","tid":747061,"uid":148718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"有無其他巴打都係咁<br />\n想搵同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c8b2cd13cdb7221df7cbf0fae482bc039dba23","tid":747061,"uid":41737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9c0d14e231fbabb87d3bd4ed78f320813cd76ee","tid":747061,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:49:21.000Z","msg":"真係 試過<br />\n屌你我講既佢永遠唔會認真聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02615baa4373f46a33d8c11bbd07a05113dde721","tid":747061,"uid":85742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf81ec9c5b8bd4f0218d186f447756a2be346e96","tid":747061,"uid":148718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"有無其他巴打都係咁<br />\n想搵同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"之前係咁<br />\n最近散埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00b84ad28aa9934bfa7e1d1100c89de0ebe936d","tid":747061,"uid":49151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:50:10.000Z","msg":"到佢唔講你先驚"},{"pid":"bd83eac26f87f491c21eacaf9f35793e43eedd31","tid":747061,"uid":23506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係咁 一齊咗6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢次次打斷我我都同佢講 你講曬我先講啦 之後佢就say sorry聽我講 佢真係好無記性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e407895c6e1fefbc1d7ac41aaabd5b6bf7163a8d","tid":747061,"uid":28713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:56:30.000Z","msg":"試過一樣情況<br />\n最後都係決定分手<br />\n因為覺得佢唔鍾意我"},{"pid":"e4cb90b9d7009ee82500cbc98af6cce350ded094","tid":747061,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:57:19.000Z","msg":"女人係鍾意講野"},{"pid":"189045ebc882c8bd0e94e342799fd2600c67656e","tid":747061,"uid":148718,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"47c8b2cd13cdb7221df7cbf0fae482bc039dba23","tid":747061,"uid":41737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"點會唔講 唉 <br />\n覺得我地位仲差過佢啲朋友 起碼佢會聽朋友講野<br />\n可能我唯一比佢啲朋友好既 就係我會聽佢講野而又洗佢聽我講野"},{"pid":"b1e2dfceb6906de7545f47721bbc12e0a973a3a2","tid":747061,"uid":148718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"189045ebc882c8bd0e94e342799fd2600c67656e","tid":747061,"uid":148718,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"47c8b2cd13cdb7221df7cbf0fae482bc039dba23","tid":747061,"uid":41737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"點會唔講 唉 <br />\n覺得我地位仲差過佢啲朋友 起碼佢會聽朋友講野<br />\n可能我唯一比佢啲朋友好既 就係我會聽佢講野而又洗佢聽我講野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:59:36.000Z","msg":"點會唔講 唉 <br />\n覺得我地位仲差過佢啲朋友 起碼佢會聽朋友講野<br />\n可能我唯一比佢啲朋友好既 就係我會聽佢講野而又唔<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>洗佢聽我講野"},{"pid":"9c23d69135dbd23570528e6eb2a6eb699f1d08e6","tid":747061,"uid":161352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"因為你無特別野分享囉"},{"pid":"19e609646d5115069c3e5240f5f3246f6c30a0f6","tid":747061,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:43:18.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲睇人架咋喎"},{"pid":"caeb39514f34838a66d541146e92afe409699875","tid":747061,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"明，有時講一d負面野，例如邊個同事唔好點點，覺得自己係情緒垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f169699f3029fb62c2d89095b56560794659b020","tid":747061,"uid":190657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"坐低認真傾，表明你都係人，需要佢聆聽同關心，再睇下佢點<br />\n如果仲係一如既往有佢講無你講，就分手la，佢都唔愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7987bfd7816c6071e54b9988524de6cc75ac456c","tid":747061,"uid":127788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/150755_a4d091c4d63b8e7c9e68019abb2db5ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F150755_a4d091c4d63b8e7c9e68019abb2db5ea.png&h=b6ea1746&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa0dd52c378b26580433addb0f3832bc7d8a0e68","tid":747061,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"雞囉"},{"pid":"54f6990d125cc490e1c7fb1a01473b0c8304e544","tid":747061,"uid":96729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:14:22.000Z","msg":"默默比左個正皮"},{"pid":"6af02c7c1b4860fec9517b1daeef7e2833feaef7","tid":747061,"uid":14165,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:36:09.000Z","msg":"我只能講 <br />\n有機會你講野好悶、好無聊、無重點 <br />\n或 講極都未入正題 <br />\n聽完又唔識回應你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我有時聽條仔講野都有啲辛苦<br />\n我雖然對佢所有嘅野 都有興趣<br />\n但佢講野遲遲唔入正題，<br />\n所以基本上次次我都係好似玩緊問答遊戲嘅<br />\n幫佢盡快入正題 + 完結話題<br />\n<br />\n絲"},{"pid":"66d59e24b870e9b56cdb354294e99e0101dffd72","tid":747061,"uid":79865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:42:41.000Z","msg":"咁你咪同佢講我未講完呀, 或者你點睇咁囉<br />\n有啲人太鍾意講野真係未必為意自己其實冇聽到人講野"},{"pid":"5c31a1b596c6a290d6ad4841c5c7f2a1de8203c8","tid":747061,"uid":7674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:43:50.000Z","msg":"有朝一日唔再同你講先上黎開po"},{"pid":"012779bb2693af2a84b3b66ce88c856f2fea5009","tid":747061,"uid":80507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"佢對關於你既事冇興趣 你有你講 佢聽完就算<br />\n唔會點認真回應你 只可以話佢份人比較自我中心<br />\nfocus係圍繞住自己既事到囉<br />\n<br />\n要認真同佢講下呢個問題 比佢知你有在意<br />\n講完都係咁既話 姐係唔中意你啦<br />\n<br />\n因為試過 好中意對方會想知所有有關於佢既事 <br />\n包括佢啲老細同事點點點 <br />\n我唔中意既 你講乜我都冇心裝載 <br />\n講完聽朝訓醒就唔撚記得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}